<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12173g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12173g">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12173g"> 173(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> fall of the leaf /(boia)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">&ldquo;The Fall of the Leaf.&rdquo;: &hellip; With the new system the floor, or the &ldquo;leaf,&rdquo; on which the person about to be launched into eternity was made to stand, stood out from the prison wall, on the outer side of which it was placed, while above it hung the iron rings through which the ropes were passed &mdash; for as many as three at least appear to have been sometimes hanged at the same moment. The condemned walked on to the leaf or platform through an open window, and when the &ldquo;leaf&rdquo; fell they fell with it. <small> <a name="FJ4oct24" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ4oct24"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (4 October 1924) 8/6</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: It. <i>boia</i>: hangman. </mm> </dd></dl>
